InfraPulse remains neutral infrastructure.

---

## Example Flows

### Autonomous SaaS Procurement

1. Agent A pays Agent B
2. Agent B submits execution receipt
3. InfraPulse verifies deterministically
4. Verdict issued
5. External system unlocks payment

---

### Swarm-Based Execution

1. Coordinator forms swarm
2. Sub-agents submit receipts
3. InfraPulse verifies bundle
4. Single aggregate verdict issued
5. Distribution handled externally

---

### Cross-Ecosystem AI Coordination

1. Agents open hash-only session
2. Transcript hash committed
3. Agreement drafted
4. Execution verified
5. Verdict issued
6. Settlement triggered externally

---

